<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-98473" number="41320" version="193">
			<HEADING>Chapter 3: Rulemaking</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-14303" name="T17C003"/>Chapter 3: Rulemaking</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="true">
			<RECORD id="0-0-0-98475" number="41321" version="2410">
				<HEADING>Subchapter A: Proposed Rules</HEADING>
				<PARA>Subchapter A: Proposed Rules</PARA>
			</RECORD>
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-136947" number="41322" version="2410">
								<HEADING>§ 15-01 Proposed Rules.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-14305" name="T17C003_15-01"/>§ 15-01 Proposed Rules.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-98476" number="41323" version="1827">
									<PARA>The chair may draft or direct to be drafted such proposed rules of the Commission as he or she may deem necessary to effectuate the provisions of Section <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="2101" destination-id="0-0-0-0">2101</LINK> of the Charter and of <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T16-a" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Title 16-A</LINK> of the Administrative Code of the City of New York, and may provide for the publication and distribution of any such proposed rule and for a public hearing on any such proposed rule, all in accordance with the requirements of <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="Chapter 45" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Chapter 45</LINK> of the Charter. No rule of the Commission will be promulgated except by vote of a majority of the Commission, in accordance with Section <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="1119" destination-id="0-0-0-0">1119</LINK> of the Charter. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-013]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-98474" number="41324" version="2410">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 4/10/2017, eff. 5/10/2017) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-013]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="true">
			<RECORD id="0-0-0-136944" number="41325" version="2410">
				<HEADING>Subchapter B: Petitions for Rulemaking</HEADING>
				<PARA>Subchapter B: Petitions for Rulemaking</PARA>
			</RECORD>
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-136946" number="41326" version="2410">
								<HEADING>§ 16-01 Definitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17908" name="T17C003_16-01"/>§ 16-01 Definitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136965" number="41327" version="2410">
									<PARA>For the purposes of this chapter, the following terms have the following meanings: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136964" number="41328" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Person.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Person&quot; means a natural person or a business entity, including but not limited to a corporation, trust, estate, partnership, cooperative, association, firm, club or society. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136963" number="41329" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Petition.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Petition&quot; means a request or application for the chair or Commission to adopt a Rule. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136962" number="41330" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Petitioner.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Petitioner&quot; means the person who files a Petition. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136961" number="41331" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Rule.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Rule&quot; shall have the meaning set forth in section 1041 of the City Administrative Procedure Act. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136960" number="41332" version="2410">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 3/27/2023, eff. 4/26/2023) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-136967" number="41333" version="2410">
								<HEADING>§ 16-02 Procedures for Submitting Petitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17910" name="T17C003_16-02"/>§ 16-02 Procedures for Submitting Petitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136959" number="41334" version="2410">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Any Person may petition the chair to consider the adoption of a Rule. The Petition may be denied if it fails to include the following information: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136958" number="41335" version="2410">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Rule to be considered, with proposed language for adoption; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136957" number="41336" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Petitioner&apos;s arguments in support of adoption of the Rule; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136956" number="41337" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(3)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Petitioner&apos;s proposal for the time period the Rule should be in effect, if applicable; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136955" number="41338" version="2410">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(4)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The name, address, telephone number, and email address of the Petitioner or his or her authorized representative; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136954" number="41339" version="2410">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(5)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The signature of Petitioner or his or her representative. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136953" number="41340" version="2410">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Any change in the name, address, telephone number, or email address of the Petitioner or his or her authorized representative must be reported to the Commission. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136952" number="41341" version="2410">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>All Petitions should be typewritten, if possible, but handwritten Petitions will be accepted provided they are legible. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136951" number="41342" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Petitions must be submitted via the email address identified on the Commission&apos;s website for the purpose of filing such Petitions, or by mailing or delivering the Petition to the Commission&apos;s General Counsel, 100 Church St., 20th Fl., New York, NY 10007. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136950" number="41343" version="2410">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 3/27/2023, eff. 4/26/2023) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-136966" number="41344" version="2410">
								<HEADING>§ 16-03 Procedures for Consideration of and Responses to Petitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17912" name="T17C003_16-03"/>§ 16-03 Procedures for Consideration of and Responses to Petitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136949" number="41345" version="2497">
									<PARA>If a Petition is submitted in proper form, the chair may, at the chair&apos;s discretion, deny the Petition, grant the Petition in Part or grant the Petition in its entirety. The chair&apos;s determination will be in writing to the Petitioner within 60 days from the date the Petition was received. If the Petition is granted entirely or in part, the chair&apos;s determination will state the Commission&apos;s intention to initiate rulemaking by a specified date. The chair is not bound by the language proposed by Petitioner but may amend or modify such proposed language at the chair&apos;s discretion. No rule of the Commission will be promulgated except by vote of a majority of the Commission, in accordance with Section <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="1119" destination-id="0-0-0-0">1119</LINK> of the Charter. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-136945" number="41346" version="2410">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 3/27/2023, eff. 4/26/2023) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-083]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>